               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     <p>I) Selection of chants mainly of the types ˀǝsmä lä-ˁaläm and ˁǝzl (fols. <locus from="00" to="39v"/>), possibly excerpts from the Dǝggwa</p>
                     <p>Production unit I </p>
                     <p>Fols. <locus from="00v" to="9r"/>
                     </p>
                     <p>Production unit II </p>
                     <p>Fols. <locus from="10r" to="34r"/>
                     </p>
                     <p>Production unit III</p>
                     <p>Fols. <locus from="35r" to="39v"/>
                     </p>
                     
                     
                     
                  </summary>
                
               </msContents>
