                        <condition key="other">
                           <p>The first folio and the last three folios are strongly discoloured; the text on the recto-side of the first and the verso-side of the last folio is unreadable. The black ink of hand <locus target="#2"/>is bleak. Many folios are affected by humidity or water (esp. fols. <locus target="#22"/>
                              <locus from="29r" to="30v"/>, <locus from="32r" to="34v"/>). Fol. <locus target="#36"/>has a big round hole.</p>
                           
