                  <handDesc>
                     <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">19th-century scripts;  careful hands Production unit I Hand 1: fols. 00v-2v line 12 Hand 2: fols. 2v-9v (possibly more than one hand)  Production unit II Hand 3: fols. 10r-34r Production unit III Several hands<note>
